#: index.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "<firstname>Jack</firstname> <surname>Ostroff</surname>"
msgstr "<firstname>जैक</firstname> <surname>ओस्ट्रोफ्</surname> इति"

#. Tag: email
